    "DebugName": "HaulCargo_SingleToMulti2_Processed_Stims_Stanton2_SmallGrade",
    "Type": "ContractGeneratorHandler_Legacy",
    "MissionType": {
        "UUID": "ae6021b6-6a62-470e-9cc2-025f1e44ade2",
        "Name": "Hauling - Planetary"
    },
    "MissionGiver": "Covalex Independent Contractors",
    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Rank - ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Cargo Haul",
    "DisplayTitle": "Rookie Rank - Small Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nThere\u2019s a load of stims at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> ready to be picked up from a freight elevator and delivered to a few spots. They will be packaged up in containers <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> or smaller. Any chance you can knock this one out for me? \n\nDoesn\u2019t matter what order you drop them off.    \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)\n\nGlad I never picked up the habit myself because I swear I get more delivery update requests for \u201cwhere are my stims?!?\u201d than any other kind of shipment. \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi,\n\nThere\u2019s a load of stims at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> ready to be picked up from a freight elevator and delivered to a few spots. They will be packaged up in containers <EM4>4 SCU</EM4> or smaller. Any chance you can knock this one out for me? \n\nDoesn\u2019t matter what order you drop them off.    \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination1|Address]</EM4>\n\nGlad I never picked up the habit myself because I swear I get more delivery update requests for \u201cwhere are my stims?!?\u201d than any other kind of shipment. \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n[Contractor|SignOff]\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
